🐍

Odoo Snake

v19.0.420.69 LTS (Long Term Slithering)

What is this?

The world's most over-engineered snake game, built entirely inside an Odoo ERP system because someone asked "but can Odoo run games?" and we took that personally.

Features (all 100% necessary)

  • 🐍 Canvas-rendered snake with gradient body + animated eyes
  • 📦 12 collectible Odoo modules with unique install messages
  • ⚡ 5 power-ups based on actual Odoo dev commands
  • 🏆 8 achievements named after ERP project milestones
  • 💀 8 fake Python tracebacks as death messages
  • 🏅 Server-side persistent leaderboard
  • 🎵 Web Audio API 8-bit sound engine
  • ✨ Particle effects + screen shake
  • 📺 Optional CRT scanline overlay
  • 💎 Enterprise vs Community edition toggle
  • 📱 Touch/swipe controls for mobile
  • 📊 Career statistics tracking across sessions
  • 🐌 Sprint velocity: Intern → Junior → Senior → CTO
  • 🔓 sudo() mode = phase through walls
  • ⚠️ UserError() = reversed controls
  • 🔄 --dev=reload = shrinks your snake
  • 💰 Score displayed as "Revenue" because KPIs
  • 🖥️ Animated boot terminal on startup
  • 🍝 "Spaghetti Code" achievement for long snakes
  • 😰 "Go-Live Weekend" achievement for length 40

Technical Stack

React 19 + HTML5 Canvas + Web Audio API + Tailwind CSS + Odoo 19 MCP Webapp Framework + requestAnimationFrame + An irresponsible amount of engineering time

FAQ

Q: Why?
A: Why not?

Q: Is this billable?
A: Absolutely. File under "R&D."

Q: Resume-worthy?
A: "Built enterprise gaming platform on ERP infrastructure" sounds great.

Q: Story points?
A: We stopped counting at fibonacci(13).

Q: Does it scale?
A: The snake does. Horizontally. That's scaling, right?
